<li><a href='http://news.yahoo.com/white-house--gop-debt-ceiling-wish-list-only-missing-%E2%80%98birther%E2%80%99-bill-183343075.html' target="_blank">On GOP demands, White House cracks Republican wish list only missing a ‘birther bill'</a><br />
